OL,3,COrthopaedic surgeon who broke ankle on
OL,4,Ccoastal walk rescued by coastguard
OL,6,FAn orthopaedic surgeon who has treated
OL,7,Fmany broken ankles unexpectedly became
OL,8,Fa casualty himself while walking in
OL,9,FSouth Cornwall.
OL,11,FProfessor Chris Lavy, an NHS
OL,12,Fconsultant and surgeon based in Oxford
OL,13,Fwas on a four-day trip to the South
OL,14,FWest, accompanied by his dog and eight
OL,15,Ffriends.
OL,17,FOn an overcast day in January, they
OL,18,Fwere walking between the villages of
OL,19,FPar and Fowey. Despite being well-
OL,20,Fequipped for wet conditions, the walk
OL,21,Ftook a sudden turn.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
