FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1774530671
OL,3,COrthopaedic surgeon who broke ankle on
OL,4,Ccoastal walk rescued by coastguard
OL,6,FProf Lavy explained: "I saw a sheep in
OL,7,Fthe nearby field, so I called my
OL,8,Flabrador over. I put my walking sticks
OL,9,Fdown to put his lead on, but when he
OL,10,Fgave me a little tug, I slipped.
OL,12,F"My leg crumpled and I heard crack,
OL,13,Fcrack, crack. I knew immediately that
OL,14,FI'd broken my ankle."
OL,16,FChris' ankle quickly began to swell,
OL,17,Fand the pain left him unable to bear
OL,18,Fweight.
OL,26,@nD@VOUvD@UO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
