OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1774530671
OL,3,COrthopaedic surgeon who broke ankle on
OL,4,Ccoastal walk rescued by coastguard
OL,6,FThe remote location made an extraction
OL,7,Fby foot difficult, so an HM Coastguard
OL,8,Frescue helicopter was tasked to the
OL,9,Fscene.
OL,11,FChris was lifted to hospital where X-
OL,12,Frays confirmed a trimalleolar
OL,13,Ffracture, a high impact and severe
OL,14,Finjury involving breaks to the inner,
OL,15,Fouter, and rear ankle bones.
OL,17,FTo show his appreciation, Chris later
OL,18,Fsent a letter of thanks to St Austell
OL,19,FCRT, which Martin said lifted spirits
OL,20,Fand now takes pride of place at the
OL,21,Fcoastguard station.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
